foia:ProcessedRequestSection.foia:FootnoteText: The numbers shown reflect the numbers pulled from the FY2013 Annual Report in FOIA XPress. There was a discrepancy with regards to prior reporting and the numbers captured for this year's report. For this year's report, we have captured the requests received, processed and pending and the end of FY2013 on a monthly basis to demonstrate the consistency of our statistics. This will be a best-practice used by ED going forward.
